   traffic capacity, high data rate, and reliability for ensuring QoS.
   Cloud computing, Internet of things (IoT), and software-defined
   networking (SDN) have become some of the core technologies for the 5G
   network. Cloud-based services provide flexible and efficient solutions
   for information and communications technology by reducing the cost of
   investing in and managing information technology infrastructure. In
   terms of functionality, SDN is a promising architecture that decouples
   control planes and data planes to support programmability, adaptability,
