   3D virtual world platform Meshmoon to create intelligent open data 3D
   maps. A processing method is developed to enable the generation of 3D
   virtual environments from the open data of the National Land Survey of
   Finland. The article combines the elements needed in contemporary smart
   city concepts, such as the connection between attribute information and
   3D objects, and the creation of collaborative virtual worlds from open
